DIGEST
SB 152 Original 2026 Regular Session Fesi
Proposed law prohibits a person from manufacturing, distributing, selling, or offering for
sale any cell cultured food product for human consumption in Louisiana. Proposed law
defines cell cultured food product as any cultured animal tissue produced from in vitro
Page 2 of 3
